==Description==
The '''Green Shard''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Green Shard can be used, alongside [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}}, to purchase items at the [[Shard Trader|Shard Traders]].

==Mine Layout==
The Green Shard appears in the Underground as a 4x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:GreenShardMine.png|100px]]

==Trades==
Green Shards can be used to purchase the following items:
